	<string name="persistent_about_text">
	Persistent Boggle is a a variation on the
	fast paced word finding puzzle game.
	Starting with a 5x5 grid, the objective is to
	find words of length 3 or more.
	</string>
	<string name="sudoku_about_text">
	Sudoku is a logic-based number placement puzzle.
	Starting with a partially completed 9x9 grid, the
	objective is to fill the grid so that each
	row, each column, and each of the 3x3 boxes
	(also called <i>blocks</i>) contains the digits
	1 to 9 exactly once.
	</string>
	
